sequenceDiagram
    participant DEV as 👤 Developer
    participant CLI as gathon CLI
    participant ROUTER as Router
    participant PARSE as Parsers
    participant STORE as UnifiedStore<br/>.gathon/graph.db
    participant SERVER as FastMCP Server
    participant AGENT as 🤖 Claude Agent

    Note over DEV,AGENT: Phase 1 — Knowledge Graph Build

    DEV->>CLI: gathon build /repo --full --compress full
    CLI->>ROUTER: scan repository files
    ROUTER->>PARSE: route by file type
    Note over PARSE: code_graph pipeline → Tree-sitter<br/>gathon_doc → markdown/HTML<br/>gathon_pdf → pypdf<br/>gathon_image → Claude vision<br/>openapi_yaml → endpoint extractor
    PARSE->>STORE: upsert_unified_node() · upsert_unified_edge()
    STORE->>STORE: Louvain communities<br/>DFS execution flows<br/>FTS5 full-text index<br/>risk scoring
    CLI-->>DEV: ✅ 692 nodes · 4,876 edges built

    Note over DEV,AGENT: Phase 2 — MCP Server + Agent Query

    DEV->>CLI: gathon serve /repo --compress ultra
    CLI->>SERVER: FastMCP stdio server starts
    AGENT->>SERVER: query_graph(target="AuthManager.login", detail_level="index")
    SERVER->>STORE: BFS traversal · FTS5 search
    STORE-->>SERVER: raw results (800 tokens)
    SERVER->>SERVER: compress_tool_response() → 440 tokens
    SERVER->>SERVER: attach_token_meta() → adds _token_meta
    SERVER-->>AGENT: results + {estimated_tokens: 440, avg_per_result: 31}
    AGENT->>AGENT: decide: need full detail?
    AGENT->>SERVER: get_node(id, detail_level="full") — only for 2 nodes
    SERVER-->>AGENT: full node detail (180 tokens × 2)

    Note over DEV,AGENT: Phase 3 — Memory + Session Tracking

    AGENT->>SERVER: memory_save(title, content, importance=0.8)
    SERVER->>SERVER: MemoryDB.save() → ~/.gathon/memory/memory.db
    AGENT->>SERVER: memory_search(query) — next session
    SERVER-->>AGENT: top-5 observations (saves 3–5 tool calls)
